import logo from "./logo.svg";
// import "./App.css";

function App() {
    return ( <
        div className = "page__container" >
        <
        header className = "header" >
        <
        a className = "header__logo"
        href = "#" / >
        <
        /header> <
        main className = "main" >
        <
        section className = "profile" >
        <
        div className = "profile__avatar-container" >
        <
        img className = "profile__avatar-edit"
        src = "<%=require('.//images/VectorEdit.svg')%>"
        alt = "Редактировать профиль" / >
        <
        img className = "profile__avatar"
        src = "#"
        alt = "Аватар" / >
        <
        /div> <
        div className = "profile__info" >
        <
        h1 className = "profile__title" > Жак - Ив Кусто < /h1> <
        button type = "button"
        className = "profile__edit-button" / >
        <
        p className = "profile__subtitle" > Исследователь океана < /p> < /
        div > <
        button type = "button"
        className = "profile__add-button" / >
        <
        /section> <
        section >
        <
        ul className = "places" / >
        <
        /section> < /
        main > <
        footer className = "footer" >
        <
        p className = "footer__copyright" > ©2022 Mesto Russia < /p> < /
        footer > <
        div className = "popup popup_type_edit" >
        <
        div className = "popup__container" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "popup__close popup__close_edit" / >
        <
        h2 className = "popup__title" > Редактировать профиль < /h2> <
        form name = "popup-edit-form"
        className = "popup__form-container popup__form-container_type_edit"
        noValidate >
        <
        input type = "text"
        name = "name"
        id = "profile-name"
        className = "popup__edit-form popup__edit-form_type_name"
        placeholder = "Введите имя"
        minLength = { 2 }
        maxLength = { 30 }
        required / >
        <
        span className = "popup__text-error"
        id = "profile-name-error" / >
        <
        input type = "text"
        name = "about"
        id = "about"
        className = "popup__edit-form popup__edit-form_type_about"
        placeholder = "Введите описание"
        minLength = { 2 }
        maxLength = { 200 }
        required / >
        <
        span className = "popup__text-error"
        id = "about-error" / >
        <
        button type = "submit"
        className = "popup__submit popup__submit_type_save" >
        Сохранить <
        /button> < /
        form > <
        /div> < /
        div > <
        div className = "popup popup_type_add-card" >
        <
        div className = "popup__container" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "popup__close popup__close_add" / >
        <
        h2 className = "popup__title" > Новое место < /h2> <
        form name = "popup-edit-form"
        className = "popup__form-container popup__form-container_type_add"
        noValidate >
        <
        input type = "text"
        name = "name"
        id = "card-name"
        placeholder = "Название"
        className = "popup__edit-form popup__edit-form_type_card-name"
        minLength = { 2 }
        maxLength = { 30 }
        required / >
        <
        span className = "popup__text-error"
        id = "card-name-error" / >
        <
        input type = "url"
        name = "link"
        id = "link"
        placeholder = "Ссылка на картинку"
        className = "popup__edit-form popup__edit-form_type_link"
        minLength = { 6 }
        maxLength = { 200 }
        required / >
        <
        span className = "popup__text-error"
        id = "link-error" / >
        <
        button type = "submit"
        className = "popup__submit popup__submit_type_create" >
        Создать <
        /button> < /
        form > <
        /div> < /
        div > <
        div className = "popup popup_type_open-image" >
        <
        div className = "popup__picture-container" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "popup__close popup__close_img" / >
        <
        figure className = "popup__picture" >
        <
        img className = "popup__fulled-img"
        src = " "
        alt = " " / >
        <
        figcaption className = "popup__picture-title" / >
        <
        /figure> < /
        div > <
        /div> <
        div className = "popup popup_type_confirm" >
        <
        div className = "popup__container" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "popup__close popup__close_confirm" / >
        <
        h2 className = "popup__title" > Вы уверены ? < /h2> <
        form name = "popup-edit-form"
        className = "popup__form-container popup__form-container_type_confirm"
        noValidate >
        <
        div className = "popup__submit-container" >
        <
        button type = "submit"
        className = "popup__submit popup__submit_type_confirm" >
        Да <
        /button> < /
        div > <
        /form> < /
        div > <
        /div> <
        div className = "popup popup_type_update-avatar" >
        <
        div className = "popup__container" >
        <
        button type = "button"
        className = "popup__close popup__close_update-avatar" / >
        <
        h2 className = "popup__title" > Обновить аватар < /h2> <
        form name = "popup-edit-form"
        className = "popup__form-container popup__form-container_type_update-avatar"
        noValidate >
        <
        input type = "url"
        name = "link"
        id = "avatar-link"
        placeholder = "Ссылка на картинку"
        className = "popup__edit-form popup__edit-form_type_link-avatar"
        minLength = { 6 }
        maxLength = { 200 }
        required / >
        <
        span className = "popup__text-error"
        id = "avatar-link-error" / >
        <
        button type = "submit"
        className = "popup__submit popup__submit_type_update" >
        Сохранить <
        /button> < /
        form > <
        /div> < /
        div > <
        template id = "cardTemplate"
        className = "template-place" / >
        <
        /div>
    );
}

export default App;
